==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unwearied
<hw>Un*wea"ried</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not wearied; not
fatigued or tired; hence, persistent; not tiring or wearying;
indefatigable.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Un*wea"ried*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> -- <wf>Un*wea"ried*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unweary</ent>⟦br⟧
